              "content": "Fills the transport-strip slot 187 reserved above the ruler. A full-width fixed bar (Play/Pause toggle · Loop · n/N readout) drives an in-editor preview; a ▾ playhead marker sweeps the ruler, distinct from the static Active-Frame highlight. Leading HITL slice of PRD 199. Tokens-only; Light + Dark via theming.",
