                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 13,
                      "fontWeight": "700"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "pkPj1",
                      "name": "v",
                      "fill": "$--text-secondary",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "the bar is role=toolbar (\"Playback\"); Play/Pause and Loop expose aria-pressed and are keyboard-operable; the ▾ marker's motion respects prefers-reduced-motion (per-frame advances are content, instant).",
